features.text:
Surviving the Coming Crisis:

1.Make a plan. If a nuclear attack does happen, it won't be safe to venture outside for food â€” you should stay sheltered for at least 48 hours, preferably longer. Having supplies is important.

2.Stock up on non-perishable food. Non-perishables can last several years, whether it's in storage or in sustaining you after an attack.

3.Store water. Consider keeping a water supply in food-grade plastic containers. Clean the containers, then fill them with filtered and distilled water. Keep water purification supplies on hand.

4.Get communication supplies. Being able to stay informed, as well as alerting others to your position, can be vitally valuable.

5.Stockpile Weapons and reinforce your bunker. And remember you can't save everyone.

6.Survive at all costs...

Ball Park Punks Stadium Proposal:

Skaz One has made his position clear: The BPPunks Ballpark Project at
VOXELS FREE SPACE will keep our beloved Anons rooted in Voxels with a world-class ballpark and
mixed-used development that will catalyze community benefits for Voxelians in the
region. This project is bigger than baseball, with long-needed infrastructure and transportation
improvements that will allow people to move safely to and around the Stadium and
create a world-class financial district, all while protecting the economic engine of
our Metaverse. The project - with net new revenues,
equitable jobs, housing, and other direct benefits for all residents -- without risk of leaving
Parcel Owners on the hook as happened with bad sports deals of the past. The Anons have committed
to privately finance a new world-class ballpark and have it built by Skaz One with a vibrant mixed-use development, and we
commit it will include ongoing community benefits for generations of Voxelians to come...

The Tomb of The Un-Gnome Soldier...

â€œHere rests in honored glory a Gnome soldier known but to Vida and Self.â€

Please Take A Moment Of Self Reflection in the name of the anonymous sacrifices made on the field of battle in the fog of war. Those who bring light to the darkness, freedom to the enslaved and salvation to lost souls. Let your mind be clear and your heart be true and you shall find yourself on the right side of history...

â€œThese violent delights have violent ends / And in their triumph die, like fire and powder / Which as they kiss consume: the sweetest honey / Is loathsome in his own deliciousness / And in the taste confounds the appetite: / Therefore love moderately; long love doth so / Too swift arrives as tardy as too slow.â€

features.text:
Lair of the Fire Monster Mini - Game

Everything you must find is within these 6 burning parcels. Letters are in order.

Soon Voxelians you will learn, that in our hearts a fire burns, the respect of the Fire Monster you will earn if you find 6 voxels and see the word.

Clues:

 1.Inside the mind of child, they may see a fortress, in the mind of an adult, its a crate in the forest...

2.In a profession, long since lost, weapons and shoes would dearly cost, and the man may craft these shoes, but the shoes arent made for you. in his shop the walls did crack that's where you can find what you lack...

3.Trying to find water maybe a bitch, but between here and there it just dont mean shit, find what you really need inside the glitch...

4.I know the smelter is pleasing to the eyes, but don't mistake the forest for the trees, you find the word I promise, just have to read between the leaves...

5.Don't stare too long at the cube of days, there's one clue he will surely soon set ablaze, look through the doors the answer is clear, but be very careful as the lava is near...

6.If you've made it this far, you shouldn't have much trouble, the next clue is in plain site, hidden amongst the rubble...

If the word you have, then the game you've won, claim your prize send the word on twitter, DM @SkazOne
Remember the heroes and to refresh, if there are works missing.
